\\<<elseif $gelateria is 0>><div class="center"><img src="dockings/rome/icecream.jpg" width="60%"></div>
<<speech "You" "''$name'':">>
Um... excuse me, I just wanted to-<</speech>>
<<speech "nobody" "''Woman'':">>
Eee, you end of line! Wait for turn!<</speech>>
While the woman is telling you to wait for your turn, you see one of the men that were waiting walk inside of what seems to be the back of the store. The other men look briefly at him and keep waiting.

<<speech "You" "''$name'':">>
(That's weird...) Ok, sorry, sorry...<</speech>>
You walk back to the end of the line again.

<<speech "You" "''$name'':">>
(I'll have to find out what's going on in there...)<</speech>>
